<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/787789-can-anyone-translate-the-latin-phrases-in">Can anyone translate the Latin phrases in the last part of the book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_787789'><a id="like_count_community_question_787789" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/787789?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F355862.Erasure">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/787789-can-anyone-translate-the-latin-phrases-in">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/787789-can-anyone-translate-the-latin-phrases-in">Add your answer</a>
</li>
