<li class='cover' id='bookCover_45483786'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/45483786-garden-by-the-sea"><img alt="Garden by the Sea" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1557148545l/45483786._SX98_.jpg" />
